[5.0, "o", " 40 frames extracted\r\n"]
[5.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33mAgent:\u001b[0m "]
[6.0, "o", "The video shows a suburban residential street "]
[6.3, "o", "filmed from a forward-facing dashcam.\r\n\r\n"]
[6.8, "o", "At the beginning, the vehicle is stationary at an intersection.\r\n"]
[7.2, "o", "Several parked cars line both sides of the street — a white sedan\r\n"]
[7.5, "o", "on the left, a dark SUV and a silver hatchback on the right.\r\n\r\n"]
[8.0, "o", "The road surface is dry asphalt with visible lane markings.\r\n"]
[8.4, "o", "Trees with green foliage form a canopy overhead, suggesting\r\n"]
[8.7, "o", "late spring or summer. Dappled sunlight creates shadow patterns\r\n"]
[9.0, "o", "on the road.\r\n\r\n"]
[9.4, "o", "A pedestrian is visible on the right sidewalk, walking in the\r\n"]
[9.7, "o", "same direction as the vehicle. No oncoming traffic is visible.\r\n"]
[10.2, "o", "The speed limit sign shows 25 mph.\r\n"]
[11.0, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32mTime: 14.8s\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.5, "o", "\u001b[1;32m=== PASS ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
